✅ 1) Introduction to Linux OS (Must for QC)

Q1. What is Linux?

✅ Answer : Linux is an open-source operating system based on Unix, used widely in servers, 
	     development, and cloud because it is secure, stable, and fast.

📌 Why Linux is used in IT?
Free + open source
Stable for servers
Powerful CLI tools
Better performance
Easy automation with shell scripting


Q2. What is Kernel in Linux?

✅ Answer:
Kernel is the core part of OS that manages:
CPU
memory
devices
processes

